{"id":15319,"date":"2025-05-06T15:26:29","date_gmt":"2025-05-06T20:26:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/?page_id=15319"},"modified":"2026-04-22T11:21:34","modified_gmt":"2026-04-22T16:21:34","slug":"insurance-programs","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/about-the-chamber\/member-benefits\/insurance-programs\/","title":{"rendered":"Insurance Programs"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"15319\" class=\"elementor elementor-15319\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b7b95b7 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b7b95b7\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8e26aef\" data-id=\"8e26aef\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b04a452 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b04a452\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong data-start=\"282\" data-end=\"380\">Chamber Insurance Program <\/strong><\/span><\/h1>\n<h3><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong data-start=\"282\" data-end=\"380\">In partnership with Heartland Benefits Group\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"382\" data-end=\"726\">We are thrilled to announce our <strong data-start=\"414\" data-end=\"465\">partnership with Heartland Benefits Group (HBG)<\/strong>, a collaboration aimed at empowering our <strong data-start=\"507\" data-end=\"526\">Chamber Members<\/strong> with a premier <strong data-start=\"542\" data-end=\"571\">employee benefits program<\/strong>.\u00a0 This initiative is tailored to assist <strong data-start=\"611\" data-end=\"659\">small businesses in the Beaver Dam community<\/strong> by providing <strong data-start=\"673\" data-end=\"726\">Big Business Benefits on a Small Business Budget!<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8c028ac elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8c028ac\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5ad33de\" data-id=\"5ad33de\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3fb6850 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3fb6850\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/customized-1.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17110\" alt=\"Chamber Insurance Program Customized\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/customized-1.png 1080w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/customized-1-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-52ffab7\" data-id=\"52ffab7\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d47b900 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d47b900\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"794\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><em><strong data-start=\"736\" data-end=\"794\">Customized Employee Benefits\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"981\">This program was created to allow all individual member groups and their employees to <strong data-start=\"882\" data-end=\"915\">design their own benefit plan<\/strong> offering from our <strong data-start=\"934\" data-end=\"980\">wide variety of essential coverage options<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"981\">This <strong data-start=\"2110\" data-end=\"2137\">Chamber Benefit Program<\/strong> allows as few as <strong data-start=\"2155\" data-end=\"2182\">two full-time employees<\/strong> to access <strong data-start=\"2193\" data-end=\"2230\">competitive group plans and rates<\/strong>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1c6cccc elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1c6cccc\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4c0f090\" data-id=\"4c0f090\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88375ec elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"88375ec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/affordable.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17111\" alt=\"Beaver Dam Chamber Insurance Program Affordable\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/affordable.png 1080w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/affordable-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8c26aca\" data-id=\"8c26aca\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9043bfd elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9043bfd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 data-start=\"988\" data-end=\"1043\"><em><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1043\">Flexible, Affordable, and Easy Benefit Solutions<\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1329\">This flexible program offers every group choices. <strong data-start=\"1095\" data-end=\"1176\">Employers set their own Defined Contribution level (benefit allowance amount)<\/strong>, empowering employees to purchase the <strong data-start=\"1215\" data-end=\"1273\">benefits that are important to them and their families<\/strong>. This ensures the Employer will <strong data-start=\"1306\" data-end=\"1328\">maximize their ROI<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1331\" data-end=\"1478\">There are <strong data-start=\"1341\" data-end=\"1406\">no participation requirements for the Companion Life Benefits<\/strong>, which sets this program apart from other traditional benefit programs.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-dbca8e6 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"dbca8e6\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2ee76ac\" data-id=\"2ee76ac\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae07310 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ae07310\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Service.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17112\" alt=\"Beaver Dam Chamber Insurance Program Service\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Service.png 1080w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/Service-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a1a6916\" data-id=\"a1a6916\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1bacc74 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1bacc74\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 data-start=\"1485\" data-end=\"1531\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><em><strong data-start=\"1488\" data-end=\"1531\">Exceptional Service and Local Expertise<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1533\" data-end=\"1794\"><strong data-start=\"1533\" data-end=\"1562\">Service is our specialty.<\/strong><br data-start=\"1562\" data-end=\"1565\" \/>We are dedicated to providing <strong data-start=\"1595\" data-end=\"1631\">exceptional guidance and service<\/strong> in helping you implement your benefit plan. With <strong data-start=\"1681\" data-end=\"1728\">simple online enrollment and administration<\/strong>, we\u2019ve been helping businesses in <strong data-start=\"1763\" data-end=\"1776\">Wisconsin<\/strong> for <strong data-start=\"1781\" data-end=\"1793\">23 years<\/strong>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-cfc7809 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"cfc7809\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-38cbbf9\" data-id=\"38cbbf9\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e17dfd elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3e17dfd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">How it works:<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Each member group (with 2 or more employees) chooses a dollar amount that will go towards<br \/>benefits. Think of it as a gift card to the employee benefits store. The Minimum starts at only $25 per<br \/>employee per month. Employees are then empowered to spend the Employer&#8217;s &#8220;Defined Contribution&#8221; and<br \/>choose between the following 8 benefit offerings:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f4e69a8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f4e69a8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/41.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"Building Custom Insurance with the Beaver Dam Chamber &amp; Heartland Benefits Group\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-21c7bd9 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"21c7bd9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4><strong><em>\u2022 Life and AD&amp;D Insurance<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Voluntary Life Insurance<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Short Term Disability<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Hospital Indemnity<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Tele-Medicine Coverage<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Dental Insurance<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Vision Insurance<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Critical Illness Insurance<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Accident Insurance<\/em><\/strong><br \/><strong><em>\u2022 Identity Theft Protection<\/em><\/strong><\/h4>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c0f5240 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c0f5240\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a3c15d0\" data-id=\"a3c15d0\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88e6d17 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"88e6d17\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><strong>Chamber Insurance Benefit Program Overview<\/strong><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fa7a195 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fa7a195\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 1em;\">Discover how the Beaver Dam Chamber Insurance Benefit Program can help your business <\/span><em style=\"font-size: 1em;\" data-start=\"375\" data-end=\"406\">attract and retain top talent<\/em><span style=\"font-size: 1em;\"> through customizable employee benefits\u2014available <\/span><em style=\"font-size: 1em;\" data-start=\"456\" data-end=\"469\">exclusively<\/em><span style=\"font-size: 1em;\"> to Beaver Dam Chamber members.<\/span><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"502\" data-end=\"849\">In this 25-minute video, Steve Schwartzer walks you through how the program works, what makes it unique, and how easy it is to get started\u2014even for small businesses with just two full-time employees. Learn about the flexible &#8220;defined contribution&#8221; model, affordable monthly minimums, and the eight benefit offerings your employees can choose from.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-start=\"851\" data-end=\"1059\"><strong data-start=\"854\" data-end=\"884\">Watch on your own schedule<\/strong> \u2014 we know running a business is demanding.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\" data-start=\"851\" data-end=\"1059\">\u00a0<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1061\" data-end=\"1156\">This is a <em data-start=\"1071\" data-end=\"1109\">unique benefit of Chamber membership<\/em>\u2014don\u2019t miss the chance to take advantage of it.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<